            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab> [Pe]trus [de Ro]prando, Pe[trus] de Rigo, [I]ohannes de Honesto, Rodulfo
                        filio [Burgo] de Gazo. In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi salvatoris. Et
                        anno ab incarnacione eius millesimo octuagesimo septimo, imperante domno
                            <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/77">Henricus</persName>
                        filius Henrici in Italia vero anno tercio, die primo mense marcii,
                        indic(ione) decima. Plura enim existunt pacta que solo verbo manere possunt
                        set ob oc necesse est scripture vinculis anotari ne varietate temporum
                        oblivionis mandentur et iurgia generentur. Et quam profitemur nos pagina
                        tibi presenti <persName><name ref="Leo de Iohannes de Guida">Leo de Iohannes
                                de Guida</name></persName> petitore pro te et pro <persName><name
                                ref="Ermengarda">Mengarda</name></persName> iugali tua seu filiis et
                        nepotibus vestris, sub potestate et dominio <persName key="#Monks"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> monachus, socro et genitori
                        vestro, diebus vite sue per hanc paginam concedimus et confirmamus vobis
                        iuris nostri ordinatoris, idest omnes res illas que detinuid predicto Petrus
                        monachus et vos modo abetis et detinetis a nostra iure in <rs key="#Fundi"
                            >fundo</rs> qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fundi #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wine #Production #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            ref="#estates/3954">
                            <placeName
                                key="#Landed_possessions #Fundi #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wine #Production #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                                >Tiriscola</placeName></geogName> et in fundo qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fundi #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wine #Production #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            ref="#estates/3955">
                            <placeName
                                key="#Landed_possessions #Fundi #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wine #Production #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                                >Vado</placeName></geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fundi #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wine #Production #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            ref="#estates/3956">
                            <placeName
                                key="#Landed_possessions #Fundi #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wine #Production #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                                >Bagnolo</placeName></geogName> sitque in fundo qui vocatur
                            <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fundi #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wine #Production #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            ref="#estates/3957">
                            <placeName
                                key="#Landed_possessions #Fundi #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wine #Production #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                                >Cagnano</placeName></geogName>, cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Production"
                            >campis</rs>, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">arboribus</rs> et cum omnibus
                        sibi pertinentibus ut superius legitur, constituta <rs key="#Fines"
                            >territorio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/3987">Ravennate, in Decimo</geogName>,
                            <rs key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/3643"><placeName
                                ref="#places/4804">Sanctum Zacharias</placeName></orgName> et plebe
                            <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/3644"><placeName
                                ref="#places/4808">Sancti Petri in Cistino</placeName></orgName> et
                        territorio vicariatum <orgName>Sancti Mauri</orgName>, cum suarum <rs
                            key="#Confinia">in terra finibus</rs>. Dum vos petitores et vestro
                        filiorum et nepotum concedimus et confirmamus vobis predictas res abendum,
                        tenendum, possidendum, defensandum et nos ordinatoris cum nostris heredibus
                        vobis petitoris et vestris filiis et nepotibus ab omni persona hominum
                        vobiscum stare et autoriare et defensare promittimus pro aridis et <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">umidis</rs> pro omnia et ex omnibus. Pro
                        eo quia exinde call(ciarium) accepimus da vos petitores, idest libre quatuor
                        monete Veneticorum. Q(uo)D Si hec omnia sicut superius legitur non
                        observaverimus vel adimpleverimus, daturi et composituri esse promittimus
                        nos ordinatoris cum nostris heredibus vobis petitoribus vestrisque filiis et
                        nepotibus ANTE OM(n)E litis inicium aut interpellacione, pene nomine, <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi uncie due</rs> et post pena soluta, maneat
                        hanc paginam in sua firmitate. Quam veropaginam <persName key="#Tabellio"
                                ><name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> Cess(inate) scribere rogavimus et manibus
                        nostris firmavimus et tradimus, sub die et mense et indic(ione) suprascripta
                        decima. Singnum manibus sicut superius legitur. Singnum manibus Almerico de
                        Guiberto, Petrus de Roprando, Petrus filio Rigo testes de omnibus que
                        superius legitur. Singnum manibus Iohannes de Honesto, Rodulfo filio Burgo
                        de Gazo testes de omnibus ut superius legitur. Ego Ugo tabellio civitatis
                        Cess(inate) scriptor uic pagine post roboracione testium firmavi. Noticia
                        testium idest: Almerico de Guiberto, Petrus de Roprando, Petrus de Rigo,
                        Iohannes de Honesto, Rodulfo.</ab>
